extends layout.pug

block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      h1 Greetings visitor! I`m Otavio
      br
      p.lead.text-light
        | This is a website to showcase some of my projects as a Full-stack JavaScript developer. The portfololio itself is a project that was accomplished using Node, Express and Pug. The projects contained here demonstrate work using JavaScript, HTML, CSS, jQuery, AJAX and more.
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      each project in projects

        .cell
          a(href=`/project/${project.id}`)
            img.thumbnail(src=project.image_urls[0])
            h5 #{project.project_name}